title: Wrestling Hosts SIUE For Senior Night
text: David Dermer Wrestling 1/16/2025 3:20:00 PM Wrestling Hosts SIUE For Senior Night Kent, OH- The Golden Flashes will host the SIUE Cougars at 7 PM on Friday, January 17 in the MAC Center. Kent State leads the all-time series 6-2 over the Cougars. SIUE has won the last two meetings against the Flashes. The Golden Flashes will be recognizing senior Jordan Decatur for Senior night. Fans will also receive a powder blue Kent State Wrestling t-shirt and free boneless wings. Kent State will hit the road next week for duals against Lock Haven, Long Island and Clarion. The Flashes will wrestle Lock Haven on Friday, January 24 and will wrestle Long Island and Clarion on Sunday, January 26.
